{"title":"不向前走不知路远——蒙古谚语","authors":["郝苏民"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":5,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"不向前走不知路远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——蒙古谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井水不出鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枯树不开花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淋过大雨的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再害怕露水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的乌云经不住风吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨的露水经不住日晒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的骏马不在于鞍子好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的漂亮不在于衣饰好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马应当拴在明显的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话应当说给可相信的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不向前走就不知路远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不努力学习就不明白真理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔郝苏民　辑译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}